{"word":"ἔθος","slug":"ἔθος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔθος</b></el> <el>(ἔθος, εος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἔθω'><el>ἔθω</el></a>\n<p/><i>custom, habit</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐν ἔθει εἶναι</el> to be in <i>the habit</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>ἔθει</el> <i>habitually</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/>"}]}